      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to both flow and hemolysis transport equations; convergence order confirmed.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver and confirmed second-order spatial convergence. The power-law hemolysis transport equation was not subjected to MMS; achieved level 3 does not satisfy MRL 5 requirement of level 4."
