      "rationale": "Experimental flow rates and impeller speeds are documented and traceable. However, fluid temperature during bench testing deviated from body temperature by up to 4°C, introducing viscosity uncertainty not accounted for in the simulation boundary conditions. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
