      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E_rms) applied to hemolysis index predictions versus experimental measurements across all 5 operating points; uncertainty bands overlapping.",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index agrees within 18% RMS error across 5 operating points. Experimental uncertainty bars were estimated but not formally propagated using ASME PTC 19.1. Achieved level 3; required level 4 mandates formal uncertainty-inclusive comparison."
    },
